  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served each morning in the Panoramic restaurant - so you can enjoy a wide selection of continental options along side beautiful views of the sea. </p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Restaurant </strong></p>
<p>Taste the flavours of the Mediterranean at the hotel's panoramic restaurant, with views of the sea. On half board at dinner you will have a great choice of appetizers, first and second courses and a la carte deserts. They serve everything from Sardinian classics to international favourites - we couldn't resist the tiramisu. </p>
<p><strong>American Bar</strong></p>
<p><span>Have an aperitif or enjoy a snack in the lounge bar. Its a nice place for a light lunches too. </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
