  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beaches</strong></span></p>
<p>The large pool's split over two levels and is surrounded by palm trees and flowers. There's plenty of sun beds to relax on and nice shaded areas. For ultimate comfort, there's a few private gazebo beds dotted around the pool and gardens. </p>
<p>Staying here you have the beach of Campolongu right on your doorstep. It's the hotel's private white sandy beach - perfect for sunbathing and swimming. The second row sunbeds, umbrellas and beach towels are all included for you to use free of charge. If you'd prefer a sun lounger in the front row with uninterrupted sea views you can pay a local supplement of €25 per day.</p>
<p>There's more beaches to explore in the area too. Notteri, Cala Giunco and Punta Molentis beaches are just a five minute drive away. The natural marine reserve of Villasimius has rich variety of underwater flora and fauna - so it's the ideal place for<span> </span>diving and snorkelling.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Tennis court</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">General Facilities</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span>Parking </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
