  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>If you're after a chilled out holiday in an unspoiled location, look no further. Hotel Stella Maris is directly on the beach, has a large outdoor pool, panoramic restaurant and its close to the lovely village of Villasimius. </p>]]></listingDescription>
