  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Sea View Rooms </strong>are about 23m² and sleep up to three people. The extra bed is a sofa bed. These rooms have a balcony, with a rattan table and chairs - so you can sit out and enjoy the sea view. The vibrant décor, with turquoise, purple and blue accents make the rooms feel bright and inviting. Facilities include air conditioning, Wi-Fi, smart TV, desk and chairs, hairdryer, telephone, digital safe, blackout curtains.  </p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> without a balcony or sea views are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
